Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:04.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個球不知道去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:08.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 看來只能把球拿過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:12.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,慎重起見 我還是先跟真緒聯繫一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:14.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有些害羞 但還是有些能力的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.71,0:00:15.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,發送
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:24.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:38.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 這是… 日本？
