Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.20,0:00:52.20,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}偶然一瞬 想起了你的容貌模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:13.28,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}在記憶之中 你微笑著的側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:19.01,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}平淡無奇的日常 是無可替的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:23.81,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}這份思念之情 現在終於意識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.97,0:01:26.62,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你歡笑度過的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:29.43,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你爭論淚流的曾經
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:33.79,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們攜手的每一天 令人無比憐愛的每一天
