Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:14.94,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(960,834)\pos(942,0)}第九話 人生即是求生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:11.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:13.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:15.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 沒有 沒有 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:18.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都已經找了10天了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:21.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是既沒有找到球 也沒有斑鳩小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:22.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:30.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,剛來就把任務給辦砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:32.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:56.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為到了這邊 能跟雛還有杏子見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:03.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼就會變成這樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:09.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子跟雛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:27.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果只是擺著的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:29.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒 你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:37.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不要消沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:38.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.41,0:03:42.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有點像了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:50.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,任務也失敗了 我都不知道今後該怎麼辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:54.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊 說到底把你送到這種無人島上來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:56.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,斑鳩這傢伙也太廢物了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不知道她是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:03:59.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:00.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:03.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 她老是使喚我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:06.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就在這裡悠閒生活不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:09.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 她真是個笨蛋 笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊 就在這兒住段時間也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:13.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,飯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:16.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊 老是飯啊飯的 煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子你才煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:30.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟裙子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 挺合適的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:36.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,飯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 都是因為你們兩個不愛打扮啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:41.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那咱們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:49.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒 你要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:52.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說到度假就是小木屋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:04:58.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:04:59.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,飯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:02.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你就吃果凍不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:04.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經吃煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:07.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我就來做午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:11.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,給你 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:12.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,飯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:15.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說雛 你也得讓我吃一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:19.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不用急嘛 杏子也有份哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:23.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是你硬要給我 我才吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:26.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,給你 杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:44.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 看招
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:51.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:36.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你最近怎麼了 真緒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.89,0:06:38.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得你沒什麼精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然說是度假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:44.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但這只不過是孤島求生罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:49.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊 這是個能好好休息的時間呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:50.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不對啊 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:51.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:56.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我一直一個人在這裡 之後該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:01.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不是在這兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:06.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真緒我不是一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:19.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個 不是杏子跟雛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:25.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只是兩隻椰子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:29.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,飯……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:41.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好想見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:44.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,人類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:52.95,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs100\blur5\bord4\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1407.333,704)}超能力女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:57.95,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1200)\fs100\shad0\blur5\bord4\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1476.667,728)}超能力女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:58.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 我聽說內藤大哥很恐怖的 是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:02.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經是他的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:04.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他這一次進監獄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:08.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因為他一個人拿著日本刀 反殺了對面四個帶槍的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:11.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,人稱現實版劊子手內藤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我頭上這個傷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:15.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:19.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我當年忘記幫他點煙 他用煙灰缸給砸的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:23.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就憑這些就能拍黑幫片了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對別惹他生氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:26.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:41.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見啊 新田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:42.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:45.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱們去看看老爹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:46.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:49.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他已經意識不清了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:54.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該聽說老爹要隱退了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:55.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:09:00.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但他卻在指定接班人之前突然就昏迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:01.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎麼了 老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:07.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就說怎麼有點臭 他就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你把老年臭說得委婉一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:13.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是雛把老爹弄得意識不清的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:16.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很明顯 我會是接班人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:19.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但在我接管之前 還得先統一組內力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:24.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起來 我好像還讓你去當打手做了不少亂來的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:27.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:29.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不是好像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:33.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我這也是為你好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:36.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這也算得上是我想磨練你的一片心意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說得就好像自己已經當上了組長一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:46.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,頭兒 統一組織的事情就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:47.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:51.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓頭兒當上組長 我會全力以赴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:53.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:57.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的你已經脫胎換骨了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:57.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我開心不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:02.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我首先就得跟內藤大哥商量下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:06.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要是把他拿下 組裡就會統一了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:11.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 大哥你也會支持頭兒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:15.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:19.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我為咱們組進了監獄 出來之後還不讓我往上爬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:22.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼混吃等死 讓人無法接受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:27.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 你應該會支持我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:30.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:33.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你能先放下手裡的煙灰缸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:36.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咱們現在說的不是煙灰缸的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:42.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我很理解大哥的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:44.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但能不能先忍一忍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:46.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:50.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能讓組裡亂起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:53.43,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在老頭子不知道的情況下搞得組織四分五裂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:56.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就無法面對老頭子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:56.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:11:00.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大哥為了讓老爹安心 就支持頭兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:05.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:10.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我就像是個小鬼一樣 總是隨著性子來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:10.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:14.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 你也算得上是一個合格的黑道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.32,0:11:17.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:18.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:20.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你的義氣超棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.97,0:11:23.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人誇人也太不會誇了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:29.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小弟那邊來聯繫了 說老爹好像是醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹 我想跟你說一下你的接班人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這事說一半我就暈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:39.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,得趁我還好好的就得隱退了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:42.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那您的接班人 就定為頭兒可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:43.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:46.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接班人是什麼 是魷魚乾之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:47.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 雛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:51.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,都跟你說了少說廢話了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:54.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹一副孫女來看他了的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:57.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我來撤回之前說你臭的發言了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:59.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的 我噴了除味劑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:00.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:04.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,選接班人的意思就是選出下一任老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:06.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,之後我就會變成普通的老頭子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那下一任讓新田來當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:15.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為新田是爸爸 又多個老爹不好區分嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:16.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,乾脆合在一起算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:18.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛 你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:19.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 新田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.66,0:12:21.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:24.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就讓新田來當老爹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:26.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你是她爺爺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:29.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,別一副「給你糖糖吃」的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:30.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:33.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,得趕緊跟下邊說一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.14,hinamatsuri_staff - 复制,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz23.05\pos(485.333,262)}跟班
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.14,hinamatsuri_staff - 复制,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(746.667,434.667)\frz22.47}你之後去醫院看看老爹的狀況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.14,hinamatsuri_staff - 复制,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz23.78\3c&H30593B&\c&H325540&\pos(1341.333,402.667)}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.14,hinamatsuri_staff - 复制,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz20.24\pos(1090.667,650.666)}頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.14,hinamatsuri_staff - 复制,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz22.93\pos(1354.667,544.001)}老爹他醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.36,hinamatsuri_staff - 复制,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz24.74\pos(1138.667,488.666)}頭兒！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.36,hinamatsuri_staff - 复制,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz23.29\pos(1234.666,728.667)}老爹指定新田為接班人了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:37.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請您不要胡鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:43.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今為止是以頭兒接任組長為前提來協助整合組內的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:47.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要為了討雛高興 就說一些會讓組裡變成一團糟的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:50.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:53.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來只要拜託給頭兒就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:54.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託您了啊 老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:57.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:01.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我過於草率地把短信發出去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:02.51,hinamatsuri_staff - 复制,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz22.71\pos(1256.533,319.6)}回復
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:02.51,hinamatsuri_staff - 复制,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz23.23\pos(1371.733,429.999)}餵你他媽到底是怎麼回事！\N到底發生什麼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:05.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「我為了儘快聯繫去了廁所」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:07.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,「那之後的對話都沒聽到」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:09.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,只能這樣辦了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:12.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 到底怎麼回事啊頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:13.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,根據跟班所說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:17.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像是利用自己的小孩取得了老爹的承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:20.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟老爹就像寵孫女一樣寵她嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:21.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,確實是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.35,0:13:23.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你這傢伙在冷靜地分析什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:26.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那混蛋瞞著我們把繼承人身份搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:28.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,連屁丁點仁義都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:31.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他是現在應該馬上去打爆的第一人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:34.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我冷靜？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:37.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你說了挺有趣的話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:42.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你在十年前內鬥的時候可是一臉溫和的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:47.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對那種叛徒 賬必須要好好算清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:48.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,用他的命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:54.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你終於醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼情況啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:01.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:05.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你所描繪的美好藍圖已經破滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:07.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好享受哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會讓你活著靜靜地沉到海底的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:13.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊跟班 他們在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:20.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想說話的話 就先舉手取得同意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:21.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可我已經變成凝固的混凝土塊了啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:24.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也直接跟他說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:26.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是有想說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:29.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哥 哥 哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:33.35,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好髒！哥是誰啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:35.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是叫你要先取得同意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:38.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:45.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 我聽說你利用小孩子教唆老爹打算成為下一任組長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:47.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:50.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然因為雛的錯老爹說了些胡話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:52.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我有好好奉勸老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:55.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他把繼承人傳給頭兒你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:15:00.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明 為了組織那麼拚命地…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真難看啊 新田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:06.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你也墮入骯髒的邪道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:08.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,至少也把壞人做到底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:11.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:14.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:17.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:19.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點對不起老爹你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:22.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我們要跟這傢伙算賬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:25.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等他沉下去之後 就拜託您再指明一次繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:27.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你們說啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:29.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是順勢開個玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:32.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他就對我大聲發火 讓我別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟新田說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:38.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂跟班 到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:39.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:42.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽了要讓大哥當繼承人之後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:45.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想著要快點聯繫你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:49.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:50.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:57.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:00.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,老爹 你說的都是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:02.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:06.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還剛誇過他「真的是確實為組內著想啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:13.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:14.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:15.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:22.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要接我的班當頭兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:24.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,膳場 雖然你是頭兒輔助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過讓新田先當著沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:27.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:28.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:31.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊看啊 一口氣升到頭兒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:35.58,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那我們來打個頭兒call吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可是值得慶祝的一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:38.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:39.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.95,0:16:45.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,頭兒 頭兒 頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:50.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,頭兒 頭兒 頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:56.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,頭兒 頭兒 頭兒……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:02.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不 快點先把我搞出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田出人頭地啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:06.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,出人頭地？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:10.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\pos(1034.667,845.333)}自從新田的個人派對之後雖然有些尷尬 但發生各種事後和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:08.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就像鰤魚長大了一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:08.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}註：ハマチ和ブリ是鰤魚的不同成長階段的名稱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田變得好吃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:15.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 你要不要給他慶祝一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:17.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田應該也會高興
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:19.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺好的嘛 升職慶祝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田為人很重義氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:23.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺應該會送點什麼做回禮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:25.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 詩子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:28.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他高興 然後 回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:30.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是長得像新田的臨時工
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:31.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是長得像新田的臨時工
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:33.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是長得像新田的臨時工
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:34.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:36.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳 能給我一杯馬提尼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:41.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我想給他慶祝不過怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我想幫人慶祝 應該怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:50.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 根據為了什麼 為了誰而慶祝情況會有所不同哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:54.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不寫出相關內容 什麼建議都沒辦法提呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:56.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,去問問認識的人怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:59.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 恍然大悟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:02.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:04.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就是生日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:07.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的話是希望收到裝有自己照片的相框
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:08.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 你這品味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那相澤你又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:15.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的話 就常理而言選花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:19.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 別用那種這人居然送花眼神的看我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:23.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,慶祝的話當然就是酒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:25.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說還能有其他的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:26.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,美佳你天天喝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:28.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是因為那個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:30.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都在慶祝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:32.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對於誕生於這世上這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:35.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,想要被招待吃自己喜歡的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候果然還是驚喜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:39.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,得好好嚇他一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:41.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 慶祝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:44.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得變得不明所以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:45.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:47.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才來這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:48.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:50.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,也聽聽我的意見啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:54.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好想弄得盛大一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:55.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,盛大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:56.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,盛大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:58.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,盛大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:01.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那就全部都做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:02.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天回來的時候要按對講機哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:06.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我要準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你這麼說我就懂 那我不就是超能力者了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:10.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:12.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要給你慶祝升職
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:14.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:15.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:16.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:22.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:25.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最後只去買需要的東西就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:27.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}高橋相框店
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:28.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}電子照片洗印
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:31.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:33.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}生剝鬼酒屋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:34.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,未成年人不能買哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:37.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:42.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花買多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.37,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.37,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.37,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}相框 相片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.37,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.37,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}酒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.37,hinamatsuri_news,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}新田喜歡的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,空瓶子倒是有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:56.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\frz17.71\pos(1023.334,804.666)}驚喜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:19:59.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}海的恩惠 多田的鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:02.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:05.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田喜歡的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:12.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}表揚雛的時候用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:16.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡的食物隻能是鮭魚子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.23,0:20:22.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不想給他太多 就擺幾顆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:24.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:31.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到雛為我慶祝的這一天會來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:32.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟之前有發生過那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:36.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不向她道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:38.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她會不會喜歡哈密瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:43.49,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛 我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:44.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:46.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:49.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在進來 可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:56.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:57.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:21:01.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 死掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:07.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:09.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是小學生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:11.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會誤以為被欺負了然後哭出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:14.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼 蠟燭和鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:17.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,鮭魚子的…妖術？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:25.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好像個木魚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.91,0:21:28.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話說雛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:50.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.99,0:22:00.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你升職頭兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.06,0:22:05.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
